Introduction to Artificial Intelligence

Artificial Intelligence is revolutionizing technology and business. Key Topics:
- Machine Learning Algorithms
- Neural Networks Architecture
- Natural Language Processing
- Computer Vision Applications

Machine learning is a powerful subset of AI that enables computers to learn from data. Deep learning uses neural networks with multiple layers to solve complex problems. Applications include image recognition, speech processing, and autonomous systems.
